7:
Later we said, "Let us go to the sacred tent of Yahweh in Jerusalem;
\q2 let us worship there in front of the throne where he is sitting."
\q1

13:
Yahweh has chosen Jerusalem;
\q1 that is where he wants to rule from.
\q1

14:
He said, "This is the city where I will live forever;
\q2 this is the place where I want to stay.
\q1

15:
I will give to the people of Jerusalem all that they need;
\q2 I will give enough food to satisfy even the poor people there.
\q1
